BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:License to Tease
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260404T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260404T213000
UID:c0dcd07e7f76be749ac0d1982518151a@mercurytheater.org
DESCRIPTION:License to Tease Saturday April 4 at 7:30pm TICKETS Velvet Tho
 rn is back at the Mercury Theater with her company Epineux Productions for
  their&nbsp\;yearly fundraiser for Burlesque Hall of Fame! Help Velvet and
  friends fundraise for the legends of burlesque\, the 20th century perform
 ers that paved the way for burlesque as we know it today. And the theme of
  the evening? 007 music! Mystery\, confidence\, sultriness\, and drama is 
 the name of the game for this evening of tease. Welcoming performers from 
 near and far\, License To Tease will showcase the talent of today while ho
 noring the performers who shaped the world of burlesque. It’s the best o
 f all worlds when it comes to a fundraising event\, a highly entertaining 
 evening that gives back in big ways to the folks we owe so much to\, the l
 egends of burlesque! Come and participate\, bring your dollars for the raf
 fle and your hollers for the performers\, and enjoy a night of dazzling bu
 rlesque (and more) at Petaluma’s premier historical theater. .fe-block-e
 1bae4ba27cb8532f3ea {mix-blend-mode: \; }
LOCATION:Mercury Theater\, 3333 Petaluma Blvd N\, Petaluma\, CA 94952
URL:https://www.mercurytheater.org/mercury-theater-calendar/woody-44wdd-re
 5h8-7xmn6-99cwt-6tdxe-ra4xk
X-SOURCE:Mercury Theater
END:VEVENT
